graph LR
    LlamaStackOp[Llama Stack Operator]

    %% External Dependencies
    LlamaStackOp -->|runtime platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.20+]
    LlamaStackOp -->|operator framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.22.4]
    LlamaStackOp -->|manifest templating| Kustomize[kustomize v0.21.0]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|optional metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|optional external access| IngressController[Ingress Controller]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    LlamaStackOp -->|inference provider| Ollama[Ollama Server<br/>11434/TCP]
    LlamaStackOp -->|GPU inference provider| VLLM[vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP]
    LlamaStackOp -->|trusted CAs| TrustedCA[odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|optional networking| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| LlamaStackOp
    DataSciencePipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|automated deployment| LlamaStackOp

    %% External Services
    LlamaStackOp -->|CR management| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP]
    VLLM -->|model downloads| HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP]
    LlamaStackOp -->|image pulls| Registry[Container Registry<br/>443/TCP]

    %% Managed Resources
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates| Deployment[Deployment<br/>Llama Stack Server]
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates| Service[Service<br/>8321/TCP]
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates| HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler]
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates| PDB[PodDisruptionBudget]
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates optional| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy]
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates optional| Ingress[Ingress]
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim]

    %% Deployment dependencies
    Deployment -->|inference| Ollama
    Deployment -->|inference| VLLM

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| LlamaStackOp

